<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'About Us' }) %>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <span class="section-title">About Webjinny</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="line-height:1.8; color:var(--text-secondary, #444); font-size:0.98rem">
      <p style="margin-bottom:18px">
        Webjinny is a real estate listing platform built to make property buying, selling, and renting
        simple and transparent. We connect property owners directly with buyers and tenants — no
        middlemen, no brokerage fees, and no unnecessary paperwork.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom:18px">
        Our mission is simple: help people find the right property faster, and help owners reach
        genuine buyers without relying on traditional broker networks. Every listing on our platform
        goes through a basic verification process before it goes live, so you can browse with confidence.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom:18px">
        Whether you're looking for an apartment, a house, a plot, or a commercial space — Webjinny
        brings together listings across Madhya Pradesh and other top cities in one place, with simple
        filters to help you find exactly what you need.
      </p>

      <p>
        Have questions or want to list a property? Reach out to us on our
        <a href="/contact" style="color:var(--primary, #002FA7); font-weight:600">Contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
